item.content:encoded: This page is meant to showcase the Iota Kappa Chapter of Kappa Kappa Psi at Boise State University in Boise, Idaho. Here you will find a gallery of our members and events, list of service projects, events hosted, and awards received throughout our installment as a chapter.

The members of our chapter have participated heavily within Western District events and leadership throughout the years of our existence. Here are just some highlights of member achievements.

Other members of our chapter that have served on a district level in some capacity include:


Jeff Gander- Vice President
Stephen Barrett- Webmaster
Jeanette McMillan- President
Alex McClean- Vice President
Arthur Aguilera- Publisher




Along with members going above and beyond chapter positions, our members have also gone above and beyond performing and participating in music outside of school/collegiate settings, such as WGI and DCI ! Here are just a few of our members who have performed in these types of outside groups.
